                        ...and more elements not fully ironed out.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="row mx-auto">
                    <p class="mx-auto text-center mb-0 p-2">
                        This project is NOT projected to leave in its early stage as there's other computer projects I must attend to instead.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="row mx-auto justify-content-center mb-4">
                    @*https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/16ga2HOr1oB_mLOfUgM2SThN68KciAOTw*@

